---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-col brand-col">
        <a href="/" class="footer-logo">
          <img src="/assets/Logo-casadelsalotto.png" alt="Casa del Salotto di Farioli" width="180" height="50" />
        </a>
        <p class="address mt-2">
          Piazza Castegnate, 1<br>
          21053 Castellanza (VA)<br>
          <a href="tel:+393803104932">Tel. 3803 104 932</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Link Rapidi</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/servizi">Servizi</a></li>
            <li><a href="/storia">La Nostra Storia</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contatti">Contatti</a></li>

        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>Servizi</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/servizi/tende-su-misura">Tende su misura</a></li>
            <li><a href="/servizi/rifacimento-divani">Rifacimento divani</a></li>
            <li><a href="/servizi/tappezzeria">Tappezzeria</a></li>
            <li><a href="/servizi/materassi">Materassi</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="footer-divider" />
    
    <div class="footer-seo">
      <p>Servizi artigianali a Castellanza (VA): tende su misura, rifacimento divani, tappezzeria, materassi, tessuti d’arredo, complementi letto e mobili.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="copyright">
      &copy; {year} Casa del Salotto di Farioli.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    padding: 3rem 0 1rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    color: #444;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--primary);
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-col h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-logo img {
    height: 50px;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .mt-2 { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

  .footer-col h4 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #222;
  }

  .footer-col ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer-col a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .footer-divider {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .footer-seo p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .copyright {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
